; **********************************************************************************
; Negative test for card maize-37: compile_hex_literal used to extract via
; std::stringstream without checking the fail bit, so a malformed hex token like
; $ZZ silently stored whatever partial value operator>> left behind (often 0) with
; no diagnostic. mazm must now reject it.
; The test harness treats this file as ExpectAsmError: it passes when assembly fails.
; **********************************************************************************

$0000`0000:
    CP $ZZ R0
    HALT
